{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "Loomic API",
    "description": "Loomic backend REST API. All authenticated endpoints require a Bearer JWT obtained from `POST /auth/login`.\n\nReal-time messaging is available over **WebSocket at `ws://host:8080/ws`** (browser-friendly, JSON text frames) or over a separate **TLS TCP connection on port 9000** using a binary wire protocol.",
    "version": "0.2.0",
    "contact": {
      "name": "Loomic"
    }
  },
  "x-tcp-protocol": {
    "port": 9000,
    "transport": "TLS TCP",
    "framing": "30-byte fixed header + variable payload",
    "authentication": "First frame must be AUTH (0x02) carrying the Bearer JWT from /auth/login",
    "header": {
      "payload_len":   "uint32 LE, bytes 0-3",
      "msg_type":      "uint8, byte 4  — 0x01=CHAT 0x02=AUTH 0x03=PING 0x04=PONG 0x05=ERROR 0x06=DELETE_NOTIFY 0x07=DELIVERED 0x08=READ 0x09=TYPING",
      "flags":         "uint8, byte 5  — bit 0 (0x01) = IS_GROUP: recipient_id is a group_id; server fans-out to all group members",
      "msg_id":        "uint64 LE, bytes 6-13  — Snowflake ID assigned by server",
      "sender_id":     "uint64 LE, bytes 14-21 — Snowflake user ID of sender",
      "recipient_id":  "uint64 LE, bytes 22-29 — Snowflake user ID of recipient"
    },
    "messageSerialization": "Payload of CHAT frames is a serialized loomic.ChatMessage protobuf (see proto/chat.proto)",
    "rateLimiting":   "5 messages/second, burst of 20; excess returns ERROR frame",
    "heartbeat":      "Send PING (0x03) at least once every 30 seconds; server responds with PONG (0x04) and resets the timeout",
    "offlineDelivery": "Messages sent to offline recipients are queued in Redis and delivered on next connect"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://localhost:8080",
      "description": "Local development"
    },
    {
      "url": "http://35.232.85.186:8080",
      "description": "Production"
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "System",
      "description": "Infrastructure and liveness endpoints"
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "User registration, login, and token management"
    },
    {
      "name": "Messaging",
      "description": "Real-time chat. Connect via WebSocket at `/ws` (JSON text frames) or TLS TCP port 9000 (binary wire protocol). See x-tcp-protocol for TCP wire format."
    },
    {
      "name": "Conversations",
      "description": "Create, list, and retrieve conversation history. All endpoints require a Bearer JWT."
    },
    {
      "name": "Users",
      "description": "User discovery and profile management. All endpoints require a Bearer JWT."
    },
    {
      "name": "Groups",
      "description": "Group chat management — create groups, manage members. All endpoints require a Bearer JWT."
    },
    {
      "name": "Messages",
      "description": "Message deletion and file upload/download."
    }
  ],
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "BearerAuth": {
        "type": "http",
        "scheme": "bearer",
        "bearerFormat": "JWT",
        "description": "HS256 JWT access token (24-hour lifetime). Obtain from `POST /auth/login` and pass as `Authorization: Bearer <token>`."
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "ErrorResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["error"],
        "properties": {
          "error": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "missing required fields"
          }
        }
      },
      "HealthResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["status"],
        "properties": {
          "status": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["ok"],
            "example": "ok"
          }
        }
      },
      "RegisterRequest": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["username", "email", "password"],
        "properties": {
          "username": {
            "type": "string",
            "minLength": 1,
            "example": "alice"
          },
          "email": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "email",
            "example": "alice@example.com"
          },
          "password": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "password",
            "minLength": 6,
            "description": "Minimum 6 characters. Stored as PBKDF2-SHA256 (100k iterations).",
            "example": "supersecret123"
          }
        }
      },
      "RegisterResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["id", "username"],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Snowflake ID serialised as a decimal string.",
            "example": "7816523049238528"
          },
          "username": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "alice"
          }
        }
      },
      "LoginRequest": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["username", "password"],
        "properties": {
          "username": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "alice"
          },
          "password": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "password",
            "example": "supersecret123"
          }
        }
      },
      "RefreshRequest": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["refresh_token"],
        "properties": {
          "refresh_token": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Opaque 64-character hex token issued by `/auth/login` or a previous `/auth/refresh`.",
            "example": "a3f1b2c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2f3a4b5c6d7e8f9a0b1c2d3e4f5a6b7c8d9e0f1a2"
          }
        }
      },
      "ChatMessageResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["msg_id", "sender_id", "recipient_id", "content_b64", "msg_type", "ts_ms"],
        "properties": {
          "msg_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Snowflake message ID as a decimal string. Use as the `before` cursor for pagination.",
            "example": "7816523049238528"
          },
          "sender_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Snowflake user ID of the sender.",
            "example": "7816523049238100"
          },
          "recipient_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Snowflake user ID of the recipient.",
            "example": "7816523049238200"
          },
          "content_b64": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "byte",
            "description": "Base64-encoded raw message payload (the `content` field of the loomic.ChatMessage protobuf).",
            "example": "SGVsbG8sIHdvcmxkIQ=="
          },
          "msg_type": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "Message type: 0=CHAT, 1=AUTH, 2=PING, 3=PONG.",
            "enum": [0, 1, 2, 3],
            "example": 0
          },
          "ts_ms": {
            "type": "integer",
            "format": "int64",
            "description": "Unix timestamp in milliseconds when the server received the message.",
            "example": 1704153600000
          }
        }
      },
      "LogoutRequest": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["refresh_token"],
        "properties": {
          "refresh_token": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "The refresh token to invalidate.",
            "example": "a3f1b2c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2f3a4b5c6d7e8f9a0b1c2d3e4f5a6b7c8d9e0f1a2"
          }
        }
      },
      "CreateConversationRequest": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["member_ids"],
        "properties": {
          "member_ids": {
            "type": "array",
            "items": { "type": "string" },
            "description": "Snowflake user IDs (as strings) of other members to add. The authenticated user is always added automatically.",
            "example": ["7816523049238200"]
          }
        }
      },
      "CreateConversationResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["conv_id", "created_at"],
        "properties": {
          "conv_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Snowflake conversation ID.",
            "example": "7816523049238900"
          },
          "created_at": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time",
            "example": "2026-04-15T12:00:00Z"
          }
        }
      },
      "ConversationEntry": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["kind", "id", "last_activity_at", "unread_count"],
        "properties": {
          "kind": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["dm", "group"],
            "description": "Whether this is a direct message (dm) or group conversation."
          },
          "id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Snowflake conversation or group ID."
          },
          "last_activity_at": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "ISO 8601 timestamp of last message activity."
          },
          "last_msg_preview": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "First 128 bytes of the most recent message."
          },
          "unread_count": {
            "type": "integer",
            "description": "Number of unread messages for the authenticated user."
          },
          "peer_id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "DM only: Snowflake ID of the other user."
          },
          "peer_name": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "DM only: username of the other user."
          },
          "peer_bio": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "DM only: bio of the other user."
          },
          "peer_avatar": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "DM only: avatar URL of the other user."
          },
          "group_name": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Group only: group name."
          },
          "group_avatar": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Group only: group avatar URL."
          }
        }
      },
      "UserSearchResult": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["id", "username"],
        "properties": {
          "id": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Snowflake user ID.",
            "example": "7816523049238200"
          },
          "username": {
            "type": "string",
            "example": "bob"
          }
        }
      },
      "TokenResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "required": ["access_token", "refresh_token", "token_type"],
        "properties": {
          "access_token": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Short-lived HS256 JWT (24-hour lifetime).",
            "example": "eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiI3ODE2NTIzMDQ5MjM4NTI4IiwiaXNzIjoibG9vbWljIiwiaWF0IjoxNzA0MDY3MjAwLCJleHAiOjE3MDQxNTM2MDB9.SIGNATURE"
          },
          "refresh_token": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Opaque 64-character hex token (30-day lifetime). Rotated on every use.",
            "example": "a3f1b2c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1e2f3a4b5c6d7e8f9a0b1c2d3e4f5a6b7c8d9e0f1a2"
          },
          "token_type": {
            "type": "string",
            "enum": ["Bearer"],
            "example": "Bearer"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "responses": {
      "BadRequest": {
        "description": "Bad Request — malformed JSON or missing/invalid fields.",
        "content": {
          "application/json": {
            "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" },
            "example": { "error": "missing required fields" }
          }
        }
      },
      "Unauthorized": {
        "description": "Unauthorized — invalid credentials or expired/unknown token.",
        "content": {
          "application/json": {
            "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" },
            "example": { "error": "invalid credentials" }
          }
        }
      },
      "Conflict": {
        "description": "Conflict — username or email already registered.",
        "content": {
          "application/json": {
            "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" },
            "example": { "error": "username or email already exists" }
          }
        }
      },
      "Forbidden": {
        "description": "Forbidden — missing or invalid Bearer token, or caller is not a member of this conversation.",
        "content": {
          "application/json": {
            "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" },
            "example": { "error": "not a member of this conversation" }
          }
        }
      },
      "InternalServerError": {
        "description": "Internal Server Error — database or unexpected failure.",
        "content": {
          "application/json": {
            "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse" },
            "example": { "error": "internal server error" }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "paths": {
    "/health": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["System"],
        "operationId": "getHealth",
        "summary": "Health check",
        "description": "Returns `200 OK` with `{\"status\":\"ok\"}` when the server is alive. Safe to poll from load balancers.",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Server is healthy.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/HealthResponse" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/register": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Auth"],
        "operationId": "registerUser",
        "summary": "Register a new user",
        "description": "Creates a new user account. The password is hashed with PBKDF2-SHA256 (100 000 iterations, 128-bit salt). The returned `id` is a Snowflake ID serialised as a decimal string.",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RegisterRequest" }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "User created successfully.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RegisterResponse" }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "409": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Conflict" },
          "500": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/InternalServerError" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/login": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Auth"],
        "operationId": "loginUser",
        "summary": "Authenticate and obtain tokens",
        "description": "Validates credentials and returns a short-lived JWT access token and a 30-day opaque refresh token. Store the refresh token securely — it grants the ability to mint new access tokens.",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LoginRequest" }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Authentication successful.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TokenResponse" }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "500": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/InternalServerError" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/conversations": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Conversations"],
        "operationId": "createConversation",
        "summary": "Create a new conversation",
        "description": "Creates a conversation and adds the authenticated user plus all supplied `member_ids`. Returns the new conversation ID as a string.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/CreateConversationRequest" }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Conversation created.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/CreateConversationResponse" }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" },
          "500": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/InternalServerError" }
        }
      },
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Conversations"],
        "operationId": "listConversations",
        "summary": "List conversations for the authenticated user",
        "description": "Returns all conversations the caller is a member of, ordered newest-first. Each entry includes the other member's user ID and username.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "List of conversations.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ConversationEntry" }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" },
          "500": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/InternalServerError" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/conversations/{id}/messages": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Conversations"],
        "operationId": "getConversationMessages",
        "summary": "Fetch message history for a conversation",
        "description": "Returns up to `limit` messages from the conversation identified by `conv_id`, ordered newest-first. Use cursor-based pagination by passing the `msg_id` of the oldest message in the current page as the `before` parameter.\n\n`conv_id` is server-derived as `min(sender_id, recipient_id)` — the smaller of the two Snowflake user IDs involved in the 1-to-1 conversation.\n\nOnly members of the conversation (i.e. users who have sent or received a message in it) may access this endpoint.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Conversation ID (`conv_id` = `min(sender_id, recipient_id)`).",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "format": "int64",
              "example": 7816523049238100
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "before",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "description": "Return only messages with `msg_id` strictly less than this value. Omit (or pass `18446744073709551615`) to start from the most recent message.",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "format": "int64",
              "example": 7816523049238528
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "limit",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "description": "Maximum number of messages to return. Clamped to [1, 100]. Defaults to 50.",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "minimum": 1,
              "maximum": 100,
              "default": 50,
              "example": 50
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Message history returned successfully, newest message first.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ChatMessageResponse" }
                },
                "example": [
                  {
                    "msg_id": 7816523049238528,
                    "sender_id": 7816523049238100,
                    "recipient_id": 7816523049238200,
                    "content_b64": "SGVsbG8hIEhvdyBhcmUgeW91Pw==",
                    "msg_type": 0,
                    "ts_ms": 1704153600000
                  }
                ]
              }
            }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" },
          "500": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/InternalServerError" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/logout": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Auth"],
        "operationId": "logoutUser",
        "summary": "Invalidate a refresh token",
        "description": "Deletes the supplied refresh token from the server, preventing it from being used to mint new access tokens. The caller's access token must be valid. Returns 204 even if the token was not found (idempotent).",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LogoutRequest" }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "204": {
            "description": "Refresh token invalidated (or was already absent)."
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" },
          "500": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/InternalServerError" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/refresh": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Auth"],
        "operationId": "refreshTokens",
        "summary": "Rotate tokens using a refresh token",
        "description": "Exchanges a valid refresh token for a new access token and a new refresh token (token rotation). The old refresh token is invalidated immediately — use the new one for subsequent refreshes.",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RefreshRequest" }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Token rotation successful.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TokenResponse" }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "401": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Unauthorized" },
          "500": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/InternalServerError" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/users/search": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Users"],
        "operationId": "searchUsers",
        "summary": "Search users by username prefix",
        "description": "Returns up to `limit` users whose username starts with `q` (case-insensitive). `q` must be at least 2 characters. `limit` is clamped to [1, 20], default 10.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "q",
            "in": "query",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Username prefix to search for (minimum 2 characters).",
            "schema": { "type": "string", "minLength": 2, "example": "al" }
          },
          {
            "name": "limit",
            "in": "query",
            "required": false,
            "description": "Maximum results to return. Clamped to [1, 20]. Default 10.",
            "schema": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 20, "default": 10 }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Search results.",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "required": ["users"],
                  "properties": {
                    "users": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "items": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/UserSearchResult" }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" },
          "500": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/InternalServerError" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/users/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Users"],
        "operationId": "getUserById",
        "summary": "Get user profile",
        "description": "Returns public profile for the given user ID.",
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "User profile.",
            "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "id":         { "type": "string" },
                "username":   { "type": "string" },
                "bio":        { "type": "string" },
                "avatar_url": { "type": "string" }
              }
            }}}
          },
          "404": { "description": "User not found." }
        }
      },
      "patch": {
        "tags": ["Users"],
        "operationId": "patchUser",
        "summary": "Update own profile",
        "description": "Update `bio` and/or `avatar_url` for the authenticated user. Only the authenticated user may modify their own profile.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string" } }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "bio":        { "type": "string" },
              "avatar_url": { "type": "string" }
            }
          }}}
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": { "description": "Profile updated." },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/users/{id}/presence": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Users"],
        "operationId": "getUserPresence",
        "summary": "Get user online presence",
        "description": "Returns whether the user is currently connected. If offline, returns `last_seen_at` (ms epoch) from Redis (fast) or Postgres (durable fallback).",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Presence status.",
            "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "user_id":      { "type": "string" },
                "online":       { "type": "boolean" },
                "server_id":    { "type": "string", "nullable": true },
                "last_seen_at": { "type": "integer", "format": "int64", "nullable": true, "description": "Unix epoch in milliseconds of last disconnect. null if never seen." }
              }
            }}}
          },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/conversations/{id}/read": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Conversations"],
        "operationId": "markConversationRead",
        "summary": "Mark conversation as read",
        "description": "Clears the caller's unread count for this conversation and updates message receipts to READ status. Relays a READ frame to other online members.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string" }, "description": "Conversation or group ID." }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": { "description": "Marked as read.", "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "ok": { "type": "boolean" } } } } } },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" },
          "404": { "description": "Conversation not found." }
        }
      }
    },
    "/push/register": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Messaging"],
        "operationId": "registerDeviceToken",
        "summary": "Register device push token",
        "description": "Associates a device push token with the authenticated user for future push notifications.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["token", "platform"],
            "properties": {
              "token":    { "type": "string", "description": "Device push token." },
              "platform": { "type": "string", "enum": ["ios", "android", "web"] }
            }
          }}}
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": { "description": "Token registered.", "content": { "application/json": { "schema": { "type": "object", "properties": { "ok": { "type": "boolean" } } } } } },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" }
        }
      },
      "delete": {
        "tags": ["Messaging"],
        "operationId": "unregisterDeviceToken",
        "summary": "Unregister device push token",
        "description": "Removes the push token association.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["token"],
            "properties": {
              "token": { "type": "string" }
            }
          }}}
        },
        "responses": {
          "204": { "description": "Token unregistered." },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/groups": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Groups"],
        "operationId": "createGroup",
        "summary": "Create a group",
        "description": "Creates a group chat. The authenticated user becomes the admin. Additional members can be supplied in `member_ids`.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name"],
            "properties": {
              "name":       { "type": "string", "example": "Team Alpha" },
              "member_ids": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" } }
            }
          }}}
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Group created.",
            "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "group_id":   { "type": "string" },
                "name":       { "type": "string" },
                "created_at": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" }
              }
            }}}
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" },
          "500": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/InternalServerError" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/groups/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Groups"],
        "operationId": "getGroup",
        "summary": "Get group info and member list",
        "description": "Returns group metadata and all members. Caller must be a member.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Group details.",
            "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": {
                "group_id":   { "type": "string" },
                "name":       { "type": "string" },
                "creator_id": { "type": "string" },
                "created_at": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time" },
                "members": {
                  "type": "array",
                  "items": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "properties": {
                      "user_id":  { "type": "string" },
                      "username": { "type": "string" },
                      "role":     { "type": "string", "enum": ["admin", "member"] }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }}}
          },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" },
          "404": { "description": "Group not found." }
        }
      },
      "patch": {
        "tags": ["Groups"],
        "operationId": "patchGroup",
        "summary": "Rename group",
        "description": "Updates the group name. Caller must be an admin.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string" } }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["name"],
            "properties": { "name": { "type": "string" } }
          }}}
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": { "description": "Group renamed." },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/groups/{id}/members": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Groups"],
        "operationId": "addGroupMember",
        "summary": "Add a member to a group",
        "description": "Adds a user to the group. Caller must be an admin.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string" } }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
            "type": "object",
            "required": ["user_id"],
            "properties": { "user_id": { "type": "string" } }
          }}}
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": { "description": "Member added." },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/groups/{id}/members/{uid}": {
      "delete": {
        "tags": ["Groups"],
        "operationId": "removeGroupMember",
        "summary": "Remove a member from a group",
        "description": "Removes a member. Caller must be an admin, or the member themselves (self-remove).",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id",  "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string" } },
          { "name": "uid", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "204": { "description": "Member removed." },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/messages/{msg_id}": {
      "delete": {
        "tags": ["Messages"],
        "operationId": "deleteMessage",
        "summary": "Delete a message",
        "description": "Deletes a message from Cassandra and fans out a `DELETE_NOTIFY` frame (msg_type=0x06) to all online conversation/group members.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "msg_id", "in": "path",  "required": true,  "schema": { "type": "string" } },
          { "name": "conv_id","in": "query", "required": true,  "schema": { "type": "string" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "204": { "description": "Message deleted." },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/upload": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Messages"],
        "operationId": "uploadFile",
        "summary": "Upload a file",
        "description": "Accepts `multipart/form-data` with a `file` part. Stores the file server-side and returns a URL.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": { "multipart/form-data": { "schema": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": { "file": { "type": "string", "format": "binary" } }
          }}}
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "File uploaded.",
            "content": { "application/json": { "schema": {
              "type": "object",
              "properties": { "url": { "type": "string", "example": "/files/abc123.jpg" } }
            }}}
          },
          "400": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/BadRequest" },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" }
        }
      }
    },
    "/files/{uuid}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Messages"],
        "operationId": "getFile",
        "summary": "Download an uploaded file",
        "description": "Streams the file identified by `{uuid}` (including extension, e.g. `abc123.jpg`). Content-Type is inferred from the extension.",
        "security": [{ "BearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "uuid", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": { "description": "File content." },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" },
          "404": { "description": "File not found." }
        }
      }
    },
    "/ws": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Messaging"],
        "operationId": "websocketConnect",
        "summary": "WebSocket real-time chat endpoint",
        "description": "Upgrade to a WebSocket connection for real-time chat. After the HTTP upgrade, all communication uses JSON text frames.\n\n**Authentication** — send as first frame:\n```json\n{\"type\":\"auth\",\"token\":\"<jwt>\"}\n```\n\n**Send a DM:**\n```json\n{\"type\":\"chat\",\"conv_id\":\"<str>\",\"content\":\"hello\"}\n```\n\n**Send a group message:**\n```json\n{\"type\":\"group_chat\",\"group_id\":\"<str>\",\"content\":\"hello\"}\n```\n\n**Typing indicator:**\n```json\n{\"type\":\"typing\",\"conv_id\":\"<str>\",\"is_group\":false}\n```\nServer fans out to other members: `{\"type\":\"typing\",\"conv_id\":\"<str>\",\"user_id\":\"<str>\",\"is_group\":false}`.\n\n**Mark conversation read:**\n```json\n{\"type\":\"read\",\"conv_id\":\"<str>\",\"is_group\":false}\n```\nServer clears unread count and relays: `{\"type\":\"read\",\"conv_id\":\"<str>\",\"user_id\":\"<str>\"}`.\n\n**Heartbeat:**\n```json\n{\"type\":\"ping\"}\n```\nServer responds with `{\"type\":\"pong\"}`.\n\n**Receive a message:**\n```json\n{\"type\":\"chat\",\"msg_id\":\"<str>\",\"conv_id\":\"<str>\",\"sender_id\":\"<str>\",\"content\":\"...\",\"ts_ms\":1234}\n```\n\n**Delivery receipt:**\n```json\n{\"type\":\"delivered\",\"msg_id\":\"<str>\",\"conv_id\":\"<str>\",\"user_id\":\"<str>\"}\n```\n\n**Read receipt:**\n```json\n{\"type\":\"read\",\"conv_id\":\"<str>\",\"user_id\":\"<str>\"}\n```\n\nAll IDs are decimal strings to preserve Snowflake precision in JavaScript.",
        "responses": {
          "101": {
            "description": "Switching Protocols — WebSocket connection established."
          },
          "403": { "$ref": "#/components/responses/Forbidden" }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
